AFAnalysisRule.ConfigString: EnergyUsage := if BadVal(PrevVal('{18b832ba-9eca-48d8-9b95-a13ec9c0d446};Energy Usage','*')) then 10 else PrevVal('{18b832ba-9eca-48d8-9b95-a13ec9c0d446};Energy Usage','*'); BrownianOscillator := Max(0, EnergyUsage + Normalrnd(0,30) - 0.1*(EnergyUsage-300));

if BadVal('{18b832ba-9eca-48d8-9b95-a13ec9c0d446};Energy Usage') then "Bad" else if '{18b832ba-9eca-48d8-9b95-a13ec9c0d446};Energy Usage' < '{dce15fa5-49c4-4118-86fe-b0b78aa474ff};Usage Limit' then "Good" else "Bad"
